Story time💜

I have been very active working for my Creator journey from more than a year now. I had my exhausting phases. I had very unmotivated days. Because from last year I was just constantly making videos. I am not getting nothing out of it. I know I love making videos and I will still continue to make videos even though I don’t get anything out of it. The love and support in the comment section in my Diem is just enough to make me work all day long for the creative journey. But PRs like this just make my day. 💜
I have been buying from plum for more than a year now. I love their face wash so much that have talked about it in most of my videos and when you get a PR from a brand that you’re actually using and love its surreal💜
This counts as an achievement for me!!

Thank you so much @plumgoodness 💜
